00:29:44,740 --> 00:29:45,980
(Ancient Jade Dealer)

447
00:29:45,980 --> 00:29:46,980
You're right.

448
00:29:47,700 --> 00:29:49,340
As the only head of the Pei family,

449
00:29:50,140 --> 00:29:51,380
I can't fall.

450
00:29:55,740 --> 00:29:56,580
Smile.

451
00:30:00,140 --> 00:30:00,980
Alright.

452
