from using its techniques.

508
00:32:52,220 --> 00:32:53,300
Do you remember?

509
00:32:53,980 --> 00:32:54,820
Young Master.

510
00:32:55,020 --> 00:32:56,340
Something terrible happened.

511
00:32:56,660 --> 00:32:58,300
Young Master. Bad news.

512
00:32:58,300 --> 00:32:59,260
What's wrong?

